m1c.pdf</a> ）<br />\n3. 寫會章，需要包括職工會名稱、辦事處地址、會員資格、如何召開及舉行會員大會等資料<br />\n4. 交表，交會章（職工會聯會全部新訂規則登記申請書<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/form/rtu/Form7F_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Fform%2Frtu%2FForm7F_c.pdf&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=e9ba5921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/form/rtu/Form7F_c.pdf</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n籌備工會支援 請聯絡 @historywillabsolveme 或 @sellbbq<br />\n如有任何現有工會有意參與未來罷工 請聯絡 @proundtobehker 或 @sugdh<br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會  | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=1f7953f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n公海 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=4921ae1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=3ac9f0a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=6546203a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33hmGRR</a>"},{"pid":"a3013a19972b1e7b93ef8839d8977117dfadac04","tid":1705834,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8401a83f9762d90e6acb559062cfdec7a97991d","tid":1705834,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:11:30.000Z","msg":"唔認同一個gp 有晒各行各業既人士<br />\n<br />\n最好係各行業有自己細gp,再細啲既gp 都得<br />\n最後各個g